The undersigned is directed to inform Members of
the Council of Ministers that Shri Morarji R. Dasalj. Minister
of Heavy Industries and Commerce & Consumer Industries, will,
henceforth, be designated as 'Minister of Commerce & Industries.!
This change will come into effect from 1st January, 1957.
